GRWM 6/30: today was an all black day, was just feeling it. 
This cropped shirt with the black trousers was too basic so we had to layer it. 
I have this vintage flounce sleeve top that I layered on top of the shirt and we let little accents of the shirt liek the collar and the long cuffs peek through for that little juxtaposition of silhouettes!!!
I think it turned out great 🤩🖤✨

Anyways I’ll be here tomorrow again, we’re really doing this!! 
Arrivederci🤪💗😂
